a lot of things.

7
00:00:26,125 --> 00:00:28,500
But now that I think about it,
on the day of the incident,

8
00:00:28,666 --> 00:00:30,000
I did not see Manqing.

9
00:00:30,666 --> 00:00:31,833
Why was her necklace there?

10
00:00:32,666 --> 00:00:33,984
Only one possibility.

11
00:00:36,291 --> 00:00:37,291
She went to find my mom.

12
00:00:38,916 --> 00:00:41,666
So there's more to your mom's suicide.

13
00:00:43,250 --> 00:00:44,250
Manqing went there

14
00:00:45,458 --> 00:00:46,166
and was killed.

15
00:00:46,875 --> 00:00:47,416
Is that so?

16
00:00:52,666 --> 00:00:54,875
Then since we share the same goal,

17
00:00:55,708 --> 00:00:56,500
I hope

18
00:00:57,666 --> 00:00:58,875
we can work together.

19
00:01:00,500 --> 00:01:02,375
Only temporarily.

20
00:01:03,666 --> 00:01:05,952
=Deep Love Love Again=
After I uncover the truth,

21
