Mr. Gu.

28
00:01:35,333 --> 00:01:36,125
Qiyan.

29
00:01:39,666 --> 00:01:40,458
Mr. Gu.

30
00:01:41,166 --> 00:01:41,958
Qiyan.

31
00:01:51,666 --> 00:01:52,875
Is it Qiyan?

32
00:01:53,166 --> 00:01:53,708
Qiyan.

33
00:01:53,791 --> 00:01:55,583
I've set up Manqing

34
00:01:55,666 --> 00:01:56,541
as you said.

35
00:01:56,541 --> 00:01:57,875
I'm begging you to let me go.

36
00:01:57,875 --> 00:01:59,083
I beg you!

37
00:01:59,708 --> 00:02:01,041
Don't keep me locked up here!

38
00:02:01,416 --> 00:02:03,291
I'm begging you.

39
00:02:20,666 --> 00:02:22,041
Can't you just come back with me?

40
00:02:23,916 --> 00:02:25,250
In Gu Qiyan's opinion,

41
00:02:25,375 --> 00:02:26,458
