42
00:02:27,333 --> 00:02:28,916
Then rather than going back with you,

43
00:02:28,916 --> 00:02:30,750
I might as well stay here

44
00:02:30,833 --> 00:02:31,458
for a while.

45
00:02:51,416 --> 00:02:52,708
Put it on.

46
00:02:53,541 --> 00:02:54,833
Then I won't worry about you.

