59
00:04:45,958 --> 00:04:46,666
I'm sorry.

60
00:04:52,041 --> 00:04:54,000
I apologize for being selfish before.

61
00:04:58,208 --> 00:04:59,500
Actually, from long ago,

62
00:04:59,666 --> 00:05:02,500
I have stopped seeing you
as Manqing's replacement.

63
00:05:08,375 --> 00:05:09,833
Can you trust me once?

64
00:05:13,250 --> 00:05:13,875
Yes.

65
00:05:22,458 --> 00:05:23,458
You are Gu Qingqing,

66
00:05:24,916 --> 00:05:25,833
not Manqing.

67
00:05:26,666 --> 00:05:28,500
We can continue to cooperate.

68
00:05:33,312 --> 00:05:37,792
♪Why can't you be mine♪

69
00:05:38,624 --> 00:05:43,904
♪Melting into my mind♪

70
00:05:46,112 --> 00:05:51,182
♪I want you, I can't deny♪

71
00:05:51,182 --> 00:05:57,376
♪Let me guess your love♪

72
00:05:59,750 --> 00:06:00,958
Go in.

73
00:06:11,808 --> 00:06:16,992
♪I want you, I can't deny♪

74
00:06:25,833 --> 00:06:27,041
Has anyone come today?

75
00:06:31,500 --> 00:06:32,291
No.

76
00:06:38,375 --> 00:06:39,125
Mr. Gu,

77
00:06:39,125 --> 00:06:39,750
when can I

78
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:40,708
go out?

79
00:06:42,916 --> 00:06:43,666
Soon.

80
00:07:10,041 --> 00:07:11,000
Hello, Qiyan.

81
00:07:11,333 --> 00:07:12,250
Where are you?

82
00:07:12,708 --> 00:07:14,250
You didn't check your phone.

83
00:07:14,708 --> 00:07:17,208
Do you know I was worried
and called you dozens of times a day?

84
00:07:17,625 --> 00:07:18,666
I'm sorry.

85
00:07:19,416 --> 00:07:20,500
My phone is broken.

86
00:07:21,708 --> 00:07:22,750
You've had fun.

87
00:07:23,125 --> 00:07:24,458
Tell me when you're coming home.

88
00:07:24,833 --> 00:07:25,666
I'll pick you up.

89
00:07:25,833 --> 00:07:27,083
Okay.

90
00:07:27,458 --> 00:07:28,291
Rest early.

91
00:07:28,916 --> 00:07:29,750
Good night.

92
00:08:01,875 --> 00:08:02,708
Qiyan.

93
00:08:04,208 --> 00:08:06,333
Let me see your true face.

94
00:08:09,666 --> 00:08:10,291
Mrs. Gu,

95
00:08:10,875 --> 00:08:12,208
this is a present for you.

96
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,500
You went out to have fun.

97
00:08:14,833 --> 00:08:16,125
Why bring me a present?

98
00:08:16,458 --> 00:08:18,041
It's nothing expensive.

99
00:08:18,041 --> 00:08:19,458
Just a small present.

100
00:08:19,833 --> 00:08:21,125
It's all because of Liu Yanyan.

101
00:08:22,416 --> 00:08:23,833
After she complained to me,

102
00:08:24,250 --> 00:08:25,250
she borrowed some money,

103
00:08:25,583 --> 00:08:26,666
and then disappeared.

104
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:28,833
Liu Yanyan

105
00:08:28,833 --> 00:08:30,666
had a grudge against me at work.

106
00:08:30,833 --> 00:08:32,333
So in fact,

107
00:08:32,708 --> 00:08:34,541
it's my fault I got you into trouble.

108
00:08:35,916 --> 00:08:36,916
Miss Manqing,

109
00:08:37,250 --> 00:08:38,250
I heard

110
00:08:38,333 --> 00:08:39,625
Qiyan said

111
00:08:40,250 --> 00:08:42,125
that you went to university abroad.

112
00:08:42,333 --> 00:08:43,666
Which university was it?

113
00:08:44,625 --> 00:08:47,291
I studied philosophy at Princeton.

114
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:50,416
It has nothing to do with
finance and economics.

115
00:08:53,208 --> 00:08:54,458
Then where is your hometown?

116
00:08:54,500 --> 00:08:55,666
I'm a local.

117
00:08:55,875 --> 00:08:58,416
After moving away since I was little,

118
00:08:59,208 --> 00:09:01,666
I still have some
faint memories of this place.

119
00:09:02,833 --> 00:09:03,750
What memories?

120
00:09:06,625 --> 00:09:09,250
Sometimes I have a dream,

121
00:09:10,208 --> 00:09:12,541
in which I am drifting in the ocean.

122
00:09:12,750 --> 00:09:13,916
Through the seawater,

123
00:09:14,625 --> 00:09:16,333
I vaguely

124
00:09:17,083 --> 00:09:18,708
see an abandoned theater.

125
00:09:28,291 --> 00:09:29,291
What theater?

126
00:09:30,708 --> 00:09:32,416
I don't know what you're talking about.

127
00:09:33,583 --> 00:09:34,958
I'm sorry.

128
00:09:35,166 --> 00:09:35,791
My fault.

129
00:09:47,625 --> 00:09:48,208
Thank you.

130
00:10:16,208 --> 00:10:17,000
Manqing,

131
00:10:17,916 --> 00:10:19,083
don't bring up the theater

132
00:10:19,625 --> 00:10:20,916
in front of Mom anymore.

133
00:10:22,125 --> 00:10:22,666
Oh.

134
00:10:23,375 --> 00:10:23,791
Got it.

135
00:10:27,083 --> 00:10:28,291
Have you thought it over?

136
00:10:28,916 --> 00:10:30,791
Are you willing to accept me?

137
00:10:34,666 --> 00:10:35,541
You're right.

138
00:10:36,208 --> 00:10:38,125
Since we're not siblings now,

139
00:10:38,791 --> 00:10:39,625
why can't we

140
00:10:39,708 --> 00:10:41,041
be together?

141
00:10:45,958 --> 00:10:46,750
Manqing.

142
00:10:49,333 --> 00:10:50,958
I'll go back now.

143
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,083
You should also rest early.

144
00:10:52,875 --> 00:10:53,666
Here's your jacket.

145
00:11:13,666 --> 00:11:14,500
Hello?

146
00:11:14,500 --> 00:11:16,791
Pei Jinqing is probably using
Manqing to investigate

147
00:11:16,791 --> 00:11:17,958
what we did back then.

148
00:11:18,500 --> 00:11:19,500
How do you know?

149
00:11:19,958 --> 00:11:21,500
You just bide your time.

150
00:11:21,791 --> 00:11:23,083
Okay, I got it.
